We've made this emergency release to fix a security issue concerning System.Text.Json.

NOTICE: There won't be any updates for the v0.0.24.x series after this release, but we'll keep this version supported until January 1st, 2025.

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[*]` Fixed a security issue concerning System.Text.Json

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://github.com/Aptivi/NitrocidKS/issues/new).

